text: Seattle University (SU) is a private Jesuit university in Seattle, Washington. SU is the largest independent university in the Northwest United States, with over 7,500 students enrolled in undergraduate and graduate programs within eight schools. ==References== Category:1891 establishments in the United States Category:1890s establishments in Washington (state) Category:Colleges and universities in Washington (state) Category:Buildings and structures in Seattle
